{
  "stem": "14867.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, he entertained a lot of Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So later on, of course, he wanted me to help the other-- Genia was her name who was the main-- and he felt that, of course, I was very, very worried about it, that the Gestapo might start suspecting.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later on, as I told you, I realized that he suspected that I was Jewish, the Major.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But since he wa-- had a lot of friends, and so he really wanted to help me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he wanted me to help when the Gestapo was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on, I couldn't figure out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to myself, maybe he felt, if someone ever tells the Gestapo, here is proof that he-- because they would be very upset and maybe even killed him, if they heard that he's hiding a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he had proof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look, I even had her here when you were here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How would I know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, this kind of thinking that I had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once, they came for dinner, and an elderly officer came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked me if I might take a walk with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And went for a walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was holding me under the arms, and he was treating me differently than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was much older.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he started to show me a picture of his son, and his-- and his son looked like a Jewish guy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I started to suspect-- because, you know, there were some Jews who went to the-- to the German army under false identity.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they thought this is going to be one way of surviving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I went for a walk with him, and he started to talk.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
